Package com.tsgrp.migration.util

Contains utility functionality.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    NodeRenamer
    Abstract class which defines classes used to execute logic to update the MigrationNode.RESERVED_NAME value on a node if applicable.
    Rosetta
    Abstract class which defines classes used to translate one string to another and add translations to a translation repository (spreadsheet, database, etc); Currently used to translate old object ids into new object ids, but can be used for any generic strings.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnnotationUtil  
    AsposeUtil
    Aspose Util class that includes functionality for interacting with Aspose documents
    BatchFileFilter
    Batch File Filter.
    ExcelUtil
    Static utility methods related to Excel processing.
    ExecutionHelper
    Created by: Marc Sernatinger Date: Jan 2, 2008 Time: 1:25:13 PM ExecutionHelper is a helper class to easily spawn an external process, feed it input, check for success/error, and package the output in a number of ways.
    FilePathUtil  
    ImageAssembler
    Wrapper around the com.lowagie.text package of iText that simplifies the creation of simple PDF files.
    JdbcUtil
    JDBC helper methods.
    NodeUtil
    Static utility methods related to MigrationNode objects.
    NoSqlUtil  
    OmUtil
    Utility class to make functions available.
    PatternUtil
    Helper utility class to make pattern matching code reusable.
    PdfCopier
    Wrapper around the com.lowagie.text package of iText that simplifies the creation of simple PDF files from existing PDF files.
    RosettaCSV
    Rosetta class which translates strings stored in an CSV file.
    RosettaDatabase
    Rosetta class which translates strings stored in a database.
    RosettaExcel
    Rosetta class which translates strings stored in an Excel or CSV file.
    TokenUtil
    A utility class for converting a string with tokens such as @{object_name} with attribute values from a Node.
  • Exception Summary

Package com.tsgrp.migration.util Description

Contains utility functionality. Be sure to try to use TSGRP.jar in favor of the classes instead of adding to this class if at all possible.
